articles.author: Robert Lea
articles.title: Gaia telescope's new data reveals 'goldmine' of over 500000 undiscovered stars and more - Space.com
articles.description: The European Space Agency space telescope also found over 380 gravity-lensed quasars and detailed the orbits of over 150,000 asteroids.
